title: A small freshwater crocodile was spotted in a Northern Territory pool

title: Europe divided over Trump's Venezuela intervention and Greenland claims | 7NEWS
description: European leaders including France, Germany and Spain have condemned US military action in Venezuela as a violation of international law, while UK Prime Minister Keir Starmer faces criticism for his more cautious response. Donald Trump has reiterated interest in US control of Greenland, citing national security concerns, prompting strong pushback from Denmark's Prime Minister and Greenland's leader who have rejected the proposal. title: Brisbane's 2032 Olympic stadium architects revealed | 7NEWS
description: Australian architectural firms Cox and Hassel will partner with Japan's Azusa Sekkei to design Brisbane's new Victoria Park Stadium for the 2032 Olympic and Paralympic Games. The $3.6 billion venue will feature 63,000 seats and incorporate traditional Queenslander architectural style while connecting with the surrounding landscape. The design consortium previously delivered major sporting venues including Perth's Optus Stadium and Tokyo's National Stadium for the 2020 Games. title: Bondi attack accused moved to Goulburn Supermax | 7NEWS
description: Naveed Akram, the 24-year-old accused of the Bondi Beach terrorist attack, has been transferred from Long Bay Jail Hospital to Goulburn Supermax prison. He faces 59 charges, including 15 counts of murder and committing a terrorist act, related to the December 14th mass shooting. Goulburn Supermax is New South Wales' most secure prison facility designed for high-risk inmates.
